data.description: Absolutely adorable and UPDATED home on EXTRA LARGE CUL-DE-SAC LOT w/DECK in Desirable Newport Subdivision of Crosby close to Newport Golf Club **ROOF & CONCRETE DRIVEWAY (2015) *NO CARPET* Spacious Family RM  with lovely Brick fireplace, ceiling w/wood beams & windows w/binds. Home also features: Formal dining room, split floor plan with 2 Bedrooms & bath on one side & Master en suite w/lovely lighting & mirrors on other side. Updated Kitchen (2017) is LIGHT & BRIGHT w/White cabinets, White SUBWAY TILE Back splash, LIGHT counter tops, Wood floating shelving & opens up to breakfast & family rooms! WOW! Other updates include: Fresh and bright paint color (2016), Gorgeous updated lighting & ceiling fans (2017),  toilets (2016) & hard surface flooring throughout!! Extensive deck (2018) & replaced Fence (2018), Gutters (2019) & Front/back Door (2017) Newport offers parks, walking trails, pools, tennis courts, community & Fitness centers. Such a GREAT OPPORTUNITY/DON'T MISS IT!.
